{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a152a33222","title":"对《人民日报》社论稿《且看他们怎样动作》的批语和修改","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1320634dea","index":0,"year":1958,"month":10,"day":9,"articleId":"a152a33222"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji40","name":"毛泽东全集第40卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/40-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji40":{"comments":[{"id":"bea7eac355","publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"a152a33222","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"本篇二、三是毛泽东在审阅《人民日报》社论稿《且看他们怎样动作》时修改的两段文字。文中用宋体字排印的是毛泽东加写和改写的文字。这篇社论发表于1958年10月11日《人民日报》。"},{"id":"423b6f5137","publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"a152a33222","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"吴冷西，当时任新华通讯社社长、《人民日报》总编辑。"}],"contents":[{"id":"079cc76a9e","type":"title","text":"对《人民日报》社论稿《且看他们怎样动作》的批语和修改！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"a152a33222"},{"id":"bea7eac355","type":"paragraph","text":"退吴冷西同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"a152a33222"},{"id":"423b6f5137","type":"paragraph","text":"不算好，勉强可用。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"a152a33222"},{"id":"ed08758e15","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"a152a33222"},{"id":"48c19c5af2","type":"paragraph","text":"十月九日六时","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"a152a33222"},{"id":"9ad9ae7057","type":"paragraph","text":"中国内部的事情应当由中国人自已处理。我们的内战，三十年了。这三十年中，有一两年没有打，其余的时间都消磨在大大小小的战争中。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"a152a33222"},{"id":"81a19ad95e","type":"subtitle","text":"三","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"a152a33222"},{"id":"6b4ac052eb","type":"paragraph","text":"看来，问题尚有待于观察和考验，离解决之期尚很远。帝国主义到底是帝国主义，反动派到底是反动派。且看一看他们究竟怎样动作吧！","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"a152a33222"}],"page":{"id":"393a16ee93","publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"a152a33222","start":304,"end":305}}}},"__N_SSG":true}